snippet.title: Ace Ventura gameplay (PC Game, 1996)
snippet.description:
Introduction and gameplay for Ace Ventura (aka ace ventura: pet detective), PC game produced by 7th Level in 1996 - http://www.squakenet.com/download/ace-ventura/1455/
Interesting take on adventure game that mixes arcade and action at the same time, with the humour of Ace Ventura pet detective character.
Played through emulated Windows (Win 98/Win XP) virtual machine.
Recorded with original sound.

Similar videos you may like:
Beneath a Steel Sky - https://youtu.be/uIYgNXoK_20
Inspector Gadget - https://youtu.be/8abujZobCJI
Ace of Spades (Hentai) - https://youtu.be/D_vMHB7LO_U
